Data::RandomKeep version 0.02
================

This module helps you randomly keep a given number of offered items,
for example, 10 random lines from a file, or 6 numbers out of 49 (to
pick a lottery ticket for example).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Test::Usage for its tests.

